# Assets Loans And Receivables Advanced Amount

## identifier
de8192

## type
float

## definition
This is the value of cash physically advanced to customers by the reporting party for lending purposes during the relevant period, irrespective of whether the lending commitment arose during the relevant period or in a prior period.

## syntax
### xbrl
- balance=credit
- name=Assets.LoansAndReceivables.Advanced.Amount
- classification=baf/bafpo/bafpo5.02.05
- period=duration
